# Homepage (Sidebar + Hero Section)

The homepage (`/`) uses a split layout: a fixed sidebar and a centered hero area. Served via `app.main.read_root` -> `index.html`.

**Theme tokens (colors, typography) live in** `app/static/css/app.css` and are documented in `../ui.mdc`. Do not redefine theme values here.

## Layout

- **Grid:** `body { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr; height: 100vh; }`
- **Sidebar:** `<aside>` — fixed 120px, left-aligned.
- **Hero:** `<main>` — flexbox centered vertically and horizontally.

## Sidebar (`<aside>`)

- Container is padded (`1rem`) and separated by a right border.
- `nav > ul` contains:
  - Brand label: `<li><strong><sup>Tiny</sup><sub>Bench</sub></strong></li>`
  - Navigation links (`a.secondary`): Chat, Ranking, Power, Fight.
- Links are compact (small font, tight padding, subtle hover background).

## Hero Section (`<main>`)

- **Container:** `.hero-container` — centered column, `max-width: 600px`, `gap: 1.5rem`.
- **Title:** `<h1 class="app-name">Monitor <kbd>Power</kbd> .</h1>`
  - `<kbd>` is used as the highlight token inside the title (styling defined by theme rules; see `../ui.mdc`).
- **Input Area:** `.input-area` (width: 100%)
  - `textarea` with `min-height: 120px` and `border-radius: 8px`
  - `<small>` helper text under the textarea

